I"[&<p>I’ve been trying to understand the distributed <a href="http://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~demmel/cs267/lecture12/pdgetrf.f">block LU code written in ScaLAPACK</a>, which is written in FORTRAN. In order to understand the algorithms properly I took a 30 min crash course in FORTRAN. In this blog post I’ll write some details about the language that are relevant to understanding the ScaLAPACK code.</p>

